text: Wagi or WAGI may refer to: * Wagi, Poland * Wagi language * WAGI-LP, a low- power radio station (97.5 FM) licensed to serve Kankakee, Illinois, United States * WOSF, a radio station (105.3 FM) licensed to serve Gaffney, South Carolina, United States, which held the call sign WAGI-FM from 1971 to 2007
title: WAGI
